 <http://purl.org/dc/terms/title> "Interoperability State of Play", "eGovernment State of Play ", "Digital Public Administration Political Communications", "During the last years, the Swedish government increased its focus on interoperability and standardisation. Proof of this are the different government assignments for standardised and interoperable information and data exchange. ", "In 2016, the Government and the Swedish Association of Local Authorities and Regions (SALAR) agreed on a vision for eHealth. This vision aims to support efforts to make use of the opportunities of digitisation in social services and health care and have decided to endorse a common vision for eHealth up to 2025." .
